dat01$TotPed= dat01$NSPed+dat01$EWPed
dat01$NB_TotVol= dat01$NB_L+dat01$NB_T+dat01$NB_R
dat01$SB_TotVol= dat01$SB_L+dat01$SB_T+dat01$SB_R
dat01$EB_TotVol= dat01$EB_L+dat01$EB_T+dat01$EB_R
dat01$WB_TotVol= dat01$WB_L+dat01$WB_T+dat01$WB_R
dat01$TotVol= dat01$NB_TotVol+dat01$SB_TotVol+dat01$WB_TotVol+dat01$EB_TotVol

By Location

byLocation = dat01 %>% group_by(Location) %>% 
  summarise(TotPed1=sum(TotPed, na.rm = TRUE), 
            NB_Tot1=sum(NB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE), 
            SB_Tot1=sum(SB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE),
            EB_Tot1=sum(EB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE), 
            WB_Tot1=sum(WB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE),
            TotVol1=sum(TotVol, na.rm = TRUE))
datatable(byLocation)

by Location Date

byLocationDate = dat01 %>% group_by(Location, Date1) %>% 
  summarise(TotPed1=sum(TotPed, na.rm = TRUE), 
            NB_Tot1=sum(NB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE), 
            SB_Tot1=sum(SB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE),
            EB_Tot1=sum(EB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE), 
            WB_Tot1=sum(WB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE))
datatable(byLocationDate)

by Location Hour

byLocationHour = dat01 %>% group_by(Location, Hour) %>% 
  summarise(TotPed1=sum(TotPed, na.rm = TRUE), 
            NB_Tot1=sum(NB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE), 
            SB_Tot1=sum(SB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE),
            EB_Tot1=sum(EB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE), 
            WB_Tot1=sum(WB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE))
datatable(byLocationHour)
byLocationHour1 <- dat01 %>% group_by(Location, Hour) %>% summarise(TotPed1 = sum(TotPed)) %>%
    spread(Hour, TotPed1)
datatable(byLocationHour1)

by Location DOW

byLocationDOW = dat01 %>% group_by(Location, DOW) %>% 
  summarise(TotPedbyLoca=sum(TotPed, na.rm = TRUE), 
            NB_Tot1=sum(NB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE), 
            SB_Tot1=sum(SB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE),
            EB_Tot1=sum(EB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE), 
            WB_Tot1=sum(WB_TotVol, na.rm = TRUE))
datatable(byLocationDOW)

Pedestrian

Hourly Data

dat02 = dat01 %>% group_by(Date1, Hour) %>% summarise(NSPed1=sum(NSPed, na.rm = TRUE), EWPed1=sum(EWPed, na.rm = TRUE), TotalPed1=sum(TotPed, na.rm = TRUE))
dat03 = dat01 %>% group_by(Location, Date1, Hour) %>% summarise(NSPed1=sum(NSPed, na.rm = TRUE), EWPed1=sum(EWPed, na.rm = TRUE), TotalPed1=sum(TotPed, na.rm = TRUE))
dat04 = dat01 %>% group_by(DOW, Date1, Hour) %>% summarise(NSPed1=sum(NSPed, na.rm = TRUE), EWPed1=sum(EWPed, na.rm = TRUE), TotalPed1=sum(TotPed, na.rm = TRUE))
datatable(dat04)

# compute the calendar layout for the data frame
calendar_df <- dat04 %>%
  frame_calendar(x = Hour, y = TotalPed1, date = Date1, nrow = 4)

# ggplot
p1 <- calendar_df %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = .Hour, y = .TotalPed1, group = Date1)) +
  geom_line()+theme_bw()
prettify(p1, size = 3, label.padding = unit(0.15, "lines"))
